<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8012616>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Heisteria austroecuadorica Cornejo, Homeier & C. Ulloa. A, Inflorescence with flower buds. B, Terminal branchlet and immature fruits. C, Fruits surrounded at base by an accrescent persistent reddish-orange calyx. D, Pedicel and abaxial view of fruiting calyx. E, Abaxial view of a leafy branch and immature fruits. Photos by Jürgen Homeier, from the type population." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8012616/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

